        "en": {
            "Case created and we are escalating your case to the relevant engineer": "Case created and we are escalating your case to the relevant engineer",
            "Escalation support is required and we’ve escalated your case to a specialized team. They are now reviewing the details to ensure a swift resolution.": "Escalation support is required and we’ve escalated your case to a specialized team. They are now reviewing the details to ensure a swift resolution.",
