            "Case created and we are escalating your case to the relevant engineer": "已建立事件单，正在指派给相关工程师处理。",
            "Escalation support is required and we’ve escalated your case to a specialized team. They are now reviewing the details to ensure a swift resolution.": "需要升级支持，我们已将您的事件转移至相关团队处理，团队正在查看事情详情。",
            "Your case is currently being handled by engineer": "您的事件已有相关工程师处理。",
            "Your case has been successfully closed. \nThank you for contacting HKT EMS Service Center": "您的事件已成功关闭。\n感谢您联系HKT EMS服务中心。",
            "Onsite support is required.": "您的事件需要现场支持。",
            "Your case has been resolved by onsite engineer。": "您的事件已由现场工程师处理完成。",
            "Requested asset have been prepared.": "请求的资产已经准备完成。",
            "Status": "状态",
            "Request asset": "申请备件",
            "Transfer to onsite": "现场派单",
            "Onsite Resolve": "现场解決",
            "Expected Arrival Time": "预计到达时间",
            "New": "新工单",
            "In Progress": "处理中",
            "On Hold": "暂停",
            "Resolved": "已解决",
            "Cancelled": "取消",
        },
